这个人跟我们同样问题

但最后查到
http://jsfiddle.net/hxqrjL45/
$("#zoom_me").elevateZoom({
    zoomType : "lens", 
    lensShape : "round", 
    lensSize : 300,
    onZoomedImageLoaded:function(z){
    
 So 我们将代码改成
 onZoomedImageLoaded:function(z){
	$( ".zoomContainer" ).on( "mouseover", stopTimer );
	$( ".zoomContainer" ).on( "mouseout", startTimer );   
}

